title: Clamor Publico (O)
body: The first issue was published on May 22, 1854, and the last, which was the 170th, on January 20, 1858. Its editors were the Madeirans Antonio Correia Heredia, Dr. Antonio Gonçalves de Freitas, and Dr. Luiz de Freitas Branco.

1854: First issue of O Clamor Publico
1858: Last issue of O Clamor Publico
